    "content": "By Lauren Anikis and Julia Kim\nBALTIMORE, Maryland \u2014 Over 60 percent of children in Baltimore live in single-parent households. As one of six kids to a single mother, Everett Croslin finds additional support from his mentor, Haneef Hardy, who helps him navigate the challenges of growing up in Baltimore.",
